Description:
    Generates a person widget to display details of a CRM person. The widget only requires an
    identifier like login or email and will then display some details about this person if
    available.

Example:
    CMS: obj_class BoxPerson
    CMS: attribute sort_key (string)
    CMS: attribute person (string)

    `rails generate cms:widget:person`
    `rails generate cms:widget:person --example`